# v1.18.0 — synthetic bench fixtures are generated at runtime by
# tools/gen-bench-fixtures.mjs and must NOT be committed. They are large
# (50 MB plain text + 10000-line markdown) and would bloat the repo
# without adding any safety value. The bench harness regenerates them
# deterministically (xorshift32 seed) so the runtime cost is negligible.
*
!.gitignore
